---
title: Tofu Rice & Veggie Bowl with Toasted Sesame Dressing
description: Whip up an easy and filling rice bowl, topped with flavour in every bite. Rich coconut rice forms the base, with a nutty marinated tofu on top plus garlicky veggies for colour and crunch. With a toasted sesame dressing to bring the dish together, this is a magical medley!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5cac3b62e3f339049d748c92-cde9b19b.jpg
